header.gameNote: LITTLE CAESARS HORIZON LEAGUE MEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - FINAL

videos.description: Cleveland State's Kenny Carpenter drives to the lane, stops, spins and floats it past a defender for 2.
videos.headline: Cleveland St. wins in the post to extend early lead

videos.description: Wright State's Grant Benzinger tips a nearly intercepted pass to himself then dives out of bounds to save the turnover, running over a camera operator.
videos.headline: Wright State's Benzinger runs over cameraman to save turnover

videos.description: Tyree Appleby fakes out a defender then sinks a 3 while falling down for Cleveland State.
videos.headline: Cleveland State puts the moves on and drills 3

videos.description: Wright State's Loudon Love spins past a defender and puts the moves on another for a crafty layup.
videos.headline: Love puts the moves on Cleveland State for 2

videos.description: Head Coach Scott Nagy and the tournament's Most Outstanding Player Grant Benzinger reflect on Wright State's Horizon League championship victory over Cleveland State.
videos.headline: Nagy and Benzinger reflect on journey to championship

videos.description: Wright State hoists their championship trophy after winning the Horizon League Championship and punching their first trip to the NCAA tournament since 2007.
videos.headline: Wright State hoists Horizon League Championship trophy
